                                class="relative flex items-center self-stretch mt-[-1.00px] [font-family:'Inter-SemiBold',Helvetica] font-semibold text-[#9aa6ab] text-[13px] tracking-[0] leading-[normal]">Recipient
                                Designation</span>
                        </label>
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center relative self-stretch w-full flex-[0_0_auto]">
                            <input id="recipient-designation" name="recipient-designation" type="text" value="John Doe"
